bio:
Thorina is the leader of the notorious outlaw gang Thorina's Cutters.
She can be found in her headquarters in the tower of Cutpurse Hideout, along with her trusted bodyguards Enchanter Brecius and Snipes-Many-Innocents. She will attack intruders on sight.
She is equipped with iron armor, gauntlets and boots and is armed with her own unique Frenzy-enchanted steel warhammer.
name: Thorina
